TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {29593=Junior: Appeared in five games as a member of the varsity travel squad…Finished the season with three tackles…Made two tackles, one solo and one assist, in the Bears’ win over Bryant…Sophomore: A member of the Bears’ travel squad….Saw action against Holy Cross and Cornell...Freshman: Gained valuable experience playing for the Bears’ undefeated Junior Varsity team… Secondary School Background: A graduate of St. Edward High School where he lettered in football and track…  Phillip helped lead his team to a win in the 2010 Ohio High School Athletic Association Division I Football State Championship… Member of National Honor Society for two years and High Honor Roll for all four years… Served as senior class secretary, Student Ambassador, and Max Advantage Program Student… Personal: Phillip (Phil) Allen Smith, the son of Charles and Tiffany Smith…Has a younger sister Vanessa… Enjoys computers, building, construction, cars, technology, music, and problem solving… BEO Concentrator., 184723=Brown University Athletics | 235 Hope St. Box 1932 | Providence, RI 02912}
